This map was created for the Elite Hunterz community!

A completely unique map, something new!
Took about a month to create this map. Quite a few things are still missing, but unfortunately the engine wouldn't allow any more detail. The map is quite well optimized. A couple things here and there could be done better. A lot of the restrictions of the engine limited what I could do...

Anyway, here is a new CSS ZM map for you all.
